raw.content_description: This book describes how to configure and use the Fixed Virtual Platform (FVP) VE Cortex-A15 Cortex-A7 CCI-400 Cache Coherent Interconnect. The model enables software applications to run on a virtual implementation based on the Versatile Express (VE) memory map. The model contains a CoreTile that models an ARM Cortex-A15 SMP and an ARM Cortex-A7 SMP connected using the CCI-400.
